kaage bangara ( part : 1 ) is a kannada film directed by duniya soori . this is a prequel to critically acclaimed 2015 movie kendasampige . starring prashanth siddi in a prominent role , the movie will also have few new characters not seen in kendasampige along with a couple of artistes from kendasampige the focus of the story will be on how prasanth siddi gets hold of money which the police had seized illegally in mangalore drug raid in kendasampige . the story also revolves around three blind people produced under the banner parimala film factory , the movie has the cinematography by satya hegde and editing by deepu s. kumar . v. harikrishna is the composer of the film background-score and the soundtrack .